      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. While the mechanical components are sound and the car runs reliably, there are clear signs of use consistent with its age. The exterior features several noticeable surface scratches and a minor dent on the driver-side door. Inside, the upholstery shows some wear and minor staining, though there are no tears. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that performs well despite its cosmetic imperfections.",
