      "description": "Presenting a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic refinement. This unit has been meticulously maintained to ensure a seamless blend of performance and long-term reliability. Fully inspected and prepared for immediate delivery, it offers a superior driving experience for the professional seeking a dependable, high-caliber automobile.",
      "price": 36800.0,
